# Security headers for all pages (defense-in-depth).
# Permissions-Policy disables only features the site never uses
# (geolocation/camera/microphone/payment/usb).
# Audio playback and the "build route" link are NOT affected:
# the route opens Google Maps in a new tab, and music is playback,
# neither needs a browser permission here. autoplay is intentionally
# left unrestricted so the background music keeps working.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), camera=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=()
